description:
Manage Hiep Phuoc Factory (including power supply and automation system) by planning, organizing, and follow up maintenance of the assets and property to ensure reliable and cost-efficient operations and quality. More details as below:
- Ensure that internal and external HSEQ requirements are followed;
- Ensure that proactive maintenance work keeps or increases current production capacity and quality;
- Manage maintenance staffs by ensuring that the tasks in their areas are executed as planned according to procedures, in an efficient way, and with the right quality;
- Lead the procedure related to control the software and industrial network security for all automation system at factory;
- Lead the team in line with Leadership Expectations and tools to develop, coach, and guide its members to ensure a workforce that is competent, engaged, and enabled to meet Jotun’s current and future needs;
- Monitor and evaluate service contractors and review supplier performance (such as working with automation service provider/ experts to perform the remote service);
- Actively work together with operations to develop operations equipment to improve efficiency and/or quality;
- Coordinate maintenance work with affected area owners to plan work orders appropriately;
- Implement root cause analysis on reoccurring or critical breakdowns and failures;
- Ensure that the Matrix Maintenance System responsibility area is always up to date, at least data from work orders.

requirements:
- University graduate with technical background in Automation/ Electrical;
- At least 8 years of experience in the related fields/ industries;
- Knowledge and experience on HMI/ PLC equipment (Emerson/Siemens), Inverter, Servo motor, AutoCAD/ ISO/ CMMS (Computerized maintenance management system)/ HSE and 5S;
- Excellent management and supervisory skills;
- Ability to identify issues and determine repairs that are needed;
- Good analytical and problem-solving skills;
- Good communication, presentation skills and high level of ownership;
- Proactive approach and result focus;
- This position will be based in Hiep Phuoc Industrial Zone permanently as job requirements.


*** We offer:
- An international and professional working environment;
- Opportunities to work with Regional and Global team;
- Continuous learning opportunities and training activities through on-the-job training and our in-house learning Jotun Academy;
- Attractive compensation and benefits (13th month salary, performance bonus, allowances, etc.);

